前的短板我想还是故事的核心上面，本人的阅读量还算广，但比起各位先辈还是远远不够的，所以我会继续学习。 如果有人对这方面感兴趣可以私信我（最近期末，还要会考，看私信估计得暑假了） 项目的启动预定在高考后，目前我的重心还是学习，毕竟为了做 gal 没点其他本事，养不养的活工作室还是个问题，我不可能一辈子都是依赖父母的支持啊。 也欢迎各位大佬来敲打我们 感谢阅读！"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660364555"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I54juks3YzPEPEAMaCTEwOTAyNTUyMiCi3IS0BjAAODNALHIJNjYwMzY0NTU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1719904779.957162", "card_id": "Q_651453210", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 61}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "可不可以分享一个常用的 ai 工具？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a4f0627fa8bc3700f28f3559ffdbb37e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651453210"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI54juks3YzPEPEAMaCTEwNzA0NTEyNSDXnrOwBjAAOMUBQC1yCTY1MTQ1MzIxMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1719904779.958700", "card_id": "Q_660126726", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 93}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "去重点高中教书还是去普通高中好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "题主是今年刚毕业的硕士，本科学的电子信息，读研读的物理教学专业，算是半路出家，学科知识并不扎实，高中成绩也不好，今年考上了家乡县城的教师编，家里人都让我去一中教书 (一中校长也希望我能过去)，但我怕自己没有能力教好学生，而且本人抗压能力比较差，所以比较倾向于去普高。过几天就要远岗了还是很纠结，希望大佬们能给点意见！"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660126726"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I54juks3YzPEPEAMaCTEwODk3MjY4NiCJifezBjAAOGRALnIJNjYwMTI2NzI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcm